"{\"uid\": \"tmz.com-2024-08-11-man-climbs-eiffel-tower-olympics-closing-ceremony\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Rock climbing walls are for wusses .... so says a dude who just scaled the Eiffel Tower \\u00a0... and the timing of his stunt could not have been worse.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch the vid ... the man scales the 330-meter tower, making his way over the blue ring of the Olympics logo ... which is temporarily perched on the famed landmark.\", \"from\": 149, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some guy is climbing on the Olympic Rings at the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 343, \"end\": 356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_symbols\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.201006463836777e-22, \"text\": \"Olympic Rings\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_symbols\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_symbols\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can see him on the blue ring.Tourists are being evacuated for safety.\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Entry beneath the tower is closed.He took 'climb the Eiffel Tower' too literally!#Olympics#Paris2024@NBCOlympics@NBCNews@latimespic.twitter.com/01BFmJqTOV  The incident went down Sunday afternoon ... just 3 hours before the start of the Olympics closing ceremony, forcing French police to evacuate the area around the Tower.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 724, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.282736235488977e-18, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's unclear where the climber kicked off his ascent ... but he was spotted gaining some serious height around the tower's first viewing deck.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Visitors were escorted away by local police around 3 PM ... with some tourists even being stuck on the 2nd floor for around 30 minutes.\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Eiffel Tower has been a visible landmark during the Paris Summer Games ... a temporary stadium was built beneath the looming structure for the beach volleyball portion of the competition.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's also served as a backdrop for other events.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was heavily featured in the opening ceremony, whenCeline Dionmade hergrand returnfrom one of the tower's viewing areas.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of Sunday's events, Interior MinisterG\\u00e9rald Darmaninconfirmed 3,000 police officers will be stationed at the Stade de France ... with an additional 20,000 police troops situated throughout the City.\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1540, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1540, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the thwartedterror plotonTaylor Swift's \\\"Eras\\\" tour stop in Austria, safety is clearly paramount.\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1701, \"end\": 1708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.